OL,5,FYorath is the father of broadcaster
OL,6,FGabby Logan who recently was
OL,7,Frecognised in the New Year's Honours.
OL,9,FYorath had three other children -
OL,10,FDaniel, Louise, and Jordan. Daniel had
OL,11,Fa genetic heart condition and died in
OL,12,F1992 aged 15 while playing football at
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,FSpeaking on behalf of the family, his
OL,16,Fchildren said: "To most he was a
OL,17,Frevered footballing hero, but to us he
OL,18,Fwas Dad; a quiet, kind and gentle man.
